	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hi all My hubby(he has a 36th lvl ranger) and I are having a bit of an argument over what is the best weapons for a warrior. I have a wurmmy and a wakisashi(sp)of the frozen skies which i am duel weilding i know the wurmmy is heavy and slow but i like the damage it does. anyways he say that i need two fast swords that dont hit as hard but are faster. He also says that people will not want to group with me because i have a slower weapon in my hand. Now the argument is over why would no one want to group with me if i am hitting for 50(avg) with the wurrmy and about 11 with the frozen skies plus it procs 81 dd. I dont know do i have the wrong idea should i go with two lower damage faster swords? What do you all think?<br><br>Maeluase(still thinking of last name)<br>25th LVL Wood Elf Warrior<br>Innoruuk Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
