	   <tr><td colspan=2>This is all a matter of what your role in group is... if you are the main tank (meaning you are the one in group that the main healer is responsible for), then keeping agro is very important and, as Talupus stated, more agro is generated by faster weapons.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>However if you are not the main tank, then you want high damage so that your hits have high impact.  In this role, i would use a 2hander or the wurmy (personally i cant afford a wurmy, so use a 2hander).<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
