	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, this is a problem of personal prefrence and agro. It has been proven that faster weapons produce more agro. However people like the see their damage acually do somthing. With a wurmmy hitting high DMG they can see that. If the caster gets attacked after you attack you have to wait nearly 4 secs to get the thing off of him. Also wrummy has a nickname StaminaSlayer for it's heavy weight. Keep sta above 100 and this isn't much of a prob. Wurmys are great weps but to be an affective tank fast weapon keep agro much better than high dly/DMG weps, thus keeping your casters alive. If you are not the MA I would owever be using a 2h or wurmy they procude more DMG and you don't have to worry about keeping agro.<br><br>Islude<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
